<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>NBA Control Room</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body class="home-shell min-h-screen text-slate-100">
  <section class="flex min-h-screen">
    <%- include('partials/sidebar') %>

    <main class="home-page-main flex-1 px-4 pb-12 pt-20 md:px-8 md:pt-10">
      <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-7xl flex-col gap-8">
        <section class="home-hero overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/8 p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-cyan-950/20 backdrop-blur md:p-10">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,_rgba(56,189,248,0.22),_transparent_27%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,_rgba(249,115,22,0.16),_transparent_23%)]"></div>
          <div class="relative grid gap-8 xl:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] xl:items-end">
            <div class="space-y-5">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/25 bg-cyan-400/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-cyan-200">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-wave-square"></i>
                League Ops Console
              </span>

              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl">Run live NBA intelligence from a single command surface.</h1>
                <p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-300 md:text-lg">Monitor franchise performance, evaluate player profiles, scan injury risk, and manage your watchlist with consistent workflows built for quick analysis.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
                <a href="/team-tracker" class="home-quick-link group inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/55 px-4 py-3 transition hover:border-cyan-400/35 hover:bg-slate-900/70">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-white">Team Tracker</span>
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-cyan-300 transition group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="/players" class="home-quick-link group inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/55 px-4 py-3 transition hover:border-cyan-400/35 hover:bg-slate-900/70">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-white">Players</span>
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-cyan-300 transition group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="/injury-report" class="home-quick-link group inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/55 px-4 py-3 transition hover:border-cyan-400/35 hover:bg-slate-900/70">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-white">Injury Report</span>
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-cyan-300 transition group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="/favorite-player" class="home-quick-link group inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/55 px-4 py-3 transition hover:border-cyan-400/35 hover:bg-slate-900/70">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-white">Favorites</span>
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-cyan-300 transition group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-1 2xl:grid-cols-3">
              <article class="home-card rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/55 p-5">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">Scope</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white">4 Data Lanes</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Team, player, injury, and favorite signals connected through one navigation rail.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="home-card rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/55 p-5">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">Velocity</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white">Fast Drilldown</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Move from search to detail views with a consistent, low-friction interaction pattern.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="home-card rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/55 p-5">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">Readiness</p>
                <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white">Operational</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Your dashboard is synced and ready for real-time league tracking.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="home-media-card overflow-hidden rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/8 p-5 shadow-xl shadow-slate-950/20 backdrop-blur">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">Legacy Moment</p>
            <img src="/img/Jordan gif.gif" alt="Michael Jordan highlight" class="mt-4 h-52 w-full rounded-[1.25rem] object-cover">
          </article>
          <article class="home-media-card overflow-hidden rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/8 p-5 shadow-xl shadow-slate-950/20 backdrop-blur">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">Motion Feed</p>
            <img src="/img/ANIMATION — WalkerTKL.gif" alt="Animated basketball motion" class="mt-4 h-52 w-full rounded-[1.25rem] object-cover">
          </article>
          <article class="home-media-card overflow-hidden rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/8 p-5 shadow-xl shadow-slate-950/20 backdrop-blur md:col-span-2 xl:col-span-1">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500">Highlight Loop</p>
            <img src="/img/1959eb0193e9cf7576d222ea41165cf3.gif" alt="NBA highlight loop" class="mt-4 h-52 w-full rounded-[1.25rem] object-cover">
          </article>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </section>

  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
</body>

</html>